## Import

Import is supported using the following syntax:

The [`terraform import` command](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cli/commands/import) can be used, for example:

```
$ terraform import xray_jira_integration.cloud prod-jira-cloud
```

~> The `password` attribute is not returned by the API and will not be populated during import. You will need to set it in the configuration after import.